# Query Whitelist for RAGInbox
# Users in this list can QUERY the knowledge base and receive automated RAG replies
# via direct emails (To: bot@domain.com)
#
# Copy this file to allowed_queriers.txt and customize for your deployment
#
# One email address or domain per line
# Lines starting with # are comments
# Domain wildcards: @imperial.ac.uk (allows all @imperial.ac.uk addresses)
# Individual addresses: alice@example.com

# Example: Department-wide query access
# @yourorganization.com

# Example: Specific authorized queriers
# alice@example.com
# bob@example.com
